perl-Gtk2-GladeXML
-------------------------------------------
This package adds perl support for Glade 2.x to Gtk2-Perl.

Runtime requirements:
  cygwin-1.5.25-7
  glib2-2.14.6-1
  gtk2-x11-2.12.7-1
  libglade2-2.6.2-1
  perl-5.10.0-3
  perl-Glib-1.164-1
  perl-Gtk2-1.164-1

Build requirements:
(besides corresponding devel packages)
  binutils-20060817-1
  cygport-0.3.9-1
  gcc-core-3.4.4-3
  make-3.81-1
  perl-ExtUtils-Depends-0.205-2
  perl-ExtUtils-PkgConfig-1.10-1

Canonical homepage:
  http://gtk2-perl.sourceforge.net/

Canonical download:
  http://downloads.sourceforge.net/gtk2-perl/

-------------------------------------------

Build instructions:
  unpack perl-Gtk2-GladeXML-1.006-1-src.tar.bz2
    if you use setup to install this src package, it will be
	 unpacked under /usr/src automatically
  cd /usr/src
  cygport ./perl-Gtk2-GladeXML-1.006-1.cygport all

This will create:
  /usr/src/perl-Gtk2-GladeXML-1.006-1-src.tar.bz2
  /usr/src/perl-Gtk2-GladeXML-1.006-1.tar.bz2

-------------------------------------------

Files included in the binary package:

  /usr/lib/perl5/vendor_perl/5.10/i686-cygwin/Gtk2/GladeXML.pm
  /usr/lib/perl5/vendor_perl/5.10/i686-cygwin/Gtk2/GladeXML/Install/Files.pm
  /usr/lib/perl5/vendor_perl/5.10/i686-cygwin/Gtk2/GladeXML/Install/gladexmlperl.h
  /usr/lib/perl5/vendor_perl/5.10/i686-cygwin/Gtk2/GladeXML/Install/gladexmlperl.typemap
  /usr/lib/perl5/vendor_perl/5.10/i686-cygwin/auto/Gtk2/GladeXML/.packlist
  /usr/lib/perl5/vendor_perl/5.10/i686-cygwin/auto/Gtk2/GladeXML/GladeXML.dll
  /usr/share/doc/perl-Gtk2-GladeXML-1.006/AUTHORS
  /usr/share/doc/perl-Gtk2-GladeXML-1.006/ChangeLog
  /usr/share/doc/perl-Gtk2-GladeXML-1.006/LICENSE
  /usr/share/doc/perl-Gtk2-GladeXML-1.006/NEWS
  /usr/share/doc/perl-Gtk2-GladeXML-1.006/README
  /usr/share/man/man3/Gtk2.GladeXML.3pm.gz

------------------

Port Notes:

----- version 1.006-1 -----
Version bump, built for perl-5.10.

----- version 1.005-1 -----
New upstream release, built against perl-5.8.7 with --enable-auto-image-base.

----- version 1.004-1 -----
New upstream release, built against perl-5.8.6 with a new build script.

----- version 1.001-1 -----
Upstream bugfix release.  Changes:
* Fixed a bug that resulted in all signals being connected with
  signal_connect_after.  The scribble example works now.
* Lots of new tests.
* Documentation and example code improvements.

----- version 1.00-2 -----
Rebuilt for perl-5.8.5.

----- version 1.00-1 -----
Initial release for Cygwin.


Cygwin port maintained by:  http://cygwinports.dotsrc.org/
